text: Instinct is a 2019 Dutch drama film directed by Halina Reijn. It was screened in the Contemporary World Cinema section at the 2019 Toronto International Film Festival. It was selected as the Dutch entry for the Best International Feature Film at the 92nd Academy Awards, but it was not nominated. ==Plot== A prison therapist becomes obsessed with her charismatic patient, a violent serial rapist on the verge of being paroled. ==Cast== * Carice van Houten as Nicoline * Marwan Kenzari as Idris * Marie-Mae van Zuilen as Marieke * Pieter Embrechts as Alex * Ariane Schluter as Directrice ==See also== * List of submissions to the 92nd Academy Awards for Best International Feature Film * List of Dutch submissions for the Academy Award for Best International Feature Film ==References== ==External links== * Category:2019 films Category:2019 drama films Category:2019 psychological thriller films Category:2010s prison films Category:Dutch films Category:Dutch drama films Category:Dutch-language films
title: Instinct (2019 film)
